text:
Queens Boulevard, east side, at Van Wyck Boulevard, showing one of the boulders found here and later removed when the area was leveled out for real estate improvements.

folder: Van Wyck Boulevard & Queens Boulevard, Queens, NY
original_title: Queens: Van Wyck Boulevard - Queens Boulevard
text:
Van Wyck Boulevard, at Queens Boulevard (vantage point). The view is southeast toward 84th Drive and shows where Van Wyck Boulevard will be cut through just south of Maple Grove Cemetery. The apartment house in the background occupies the N. W. corner of 84th Drive and Manton Street. On the left (view 2) are small homes under construction, the same being visible in the background of view 3.

View 1: March 12, 1938
Views 2,3: August 11, 1940

P. L. Sperr
